### Fronius Controller (internal Web API)
### Base URL is the Haus application server

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv HAUS_BASE_URL}}

### Get inverter snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get inverter readings (default limit 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/readings
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get inverter readings with custom limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/readings?limit=50
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get power flow realtime data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/powerflow
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get inverter realtime data (CommonInverterData)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/inverter/realtimedata
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get inverter realtime data (MinMaxInverterData)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/inverter/realtimedata?dataCollection=MinMaxInverterData
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get inverter info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/inverter/info
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get active device info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/devices
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get meter realtime data (system scope)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/meter
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get meter realtime data (device scope)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/meter?scope=Device&deviceId=0
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get storage realtime data (system scope)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/storage
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get storage realtime data (device scope)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/fronius/storage?scope=Device&deviceId=0
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}
